data.description: Don't miss this AMAZING opportunity to own an all brick ranch home on a HUGE .83 acre wooded lot!! Tucked back in the peaceful Hidden Pines subdivision. Move-in ready! Beautiful wood floors sprawl throughout all main living areas and bedrooms and tile in the kitchen. NO CARPET! The living room features a gorgeous brick wood burning fireplace and lovely bay windows allowing tons of natural light to shine through. Large separate formal dining room beautifully accented with artful crown molding. Kitchen is fully equipped with stainless steel appliances and cabinet storage galore! Master Bedroom features an updated ensuite bathroom with double vanities and stunning tiled shower. The backyard provides PLENTY of space and privacy. Fully fenced and a large double gate opening to bring in all of your fun outdoor toys! Don't let this one slip away!
